Ward {3}
When King K. Rool enters, if he was cast, each player sacrifices each nonland permanent they control with mana value 2 or less.
Whenever a player sacrifices one or more permanents, you gain that much life and put that many +1/+1 counters on King K. Rool.

Flying, vigilance, ward {2}
Whenever you attack with two or more creatures, clear a stage. [i](Draw a card, then discard a card. Every third stage you clear, you clear a world, draw a card and create a Treasure token instead.)[/i]
Whenever you clear a world, return target nonland permanent with mana value 4 or less from your graveyard to the battlefield.

Ward {2}
Heroes and Nobles you control can't be blocked by creatures with power 2 or less.
Whenever Rock Mario deals combat damage to a player, untap all lands you control.
